author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Valneva ‍Total Revenues Up At 109.8 Million Euros
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - VALNEVA SE:
* ‍TOTAL REVENUES OF EUR 109.8 MILLION IN 2017 (2016 - EUR 97.9 MILLION)​
* ‍PRODUCT SALES OF EUR 92.6 MILLION IN 2017 (2016 - EUR 80.4 MILLION)​
* ‍CASH POSITION OF EUR 38.1 MILLION AT END OF 2017​ * ‍VALNEVA EXPECTS TO ANNOUNCE PHASE I TOP-LINE DATA FOR ITS LYME DISEASE VACCINE CANDIDATE IN Q1 OF 2018​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
